<paragraph blockId="0.[1220,2104,606,968]" pageId="0" pageNumber="374">• Small to medium-sized with relatively long and thick pelage, small eyes, distinctive cleft running longitudinally along muzzle that covers noseleaves, and long ears.</paragraph>
